==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Perdure
<hw>Per*dure"</hw> <pr>(p⟦etil⟧r*d⟦umac⟧r")</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>perdurare</ets>; <ets>per</ets> through +
<ets>durare</ets> to last.]</ety> <def>To last or endure for a long
time; to be perdurable or lasting.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The mind <qex>perdures</qex> while its energizing may construct a
thousand lines.</q> <rj><qau>Hickok.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Perdy</ent>⟦br⟧
